{"_id":"HattaCarter","name":"Hatta Carter - The Mad Inventor","type":"npc","img":"icons/equipment/head/top-hat-brown-striped.webp","system":{"npcType":"adversary","oppositionLevel":5,"isMainNPC":true,"attributes":{"soma":{"current":0,"max":0},"wounds":{"current":0,"max":3,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}}},"descriptors":["I am a skilled inventor, the most brilliant of my time","My emotional fragility leads me to frequent mood swings and aggressiveness"],"agenda":"I want the company of witty people and not cold automata. I long for the chats I had with Alice","gifts":[{"name":"Time Clocks","description":"Hatta can manipulate one of his clocks to influence time:\n\n1. Slow: Once per Scene, Hatta increases his OL by 2 when defending against a threat.\n\n2. Speed Up: Once per Scene, Hatta and one of his Automata can act, immediately stopping anyone's action regardless of the situation in the narrative. If an Automaton has already acted, it can act again thanks to this Gift."}],"background":"Hatta Carter is the most skilled inventor in all of England, famous for his theories on automatons. Alice Liddell hired him to research Wonder and make sense of the physics-defying nature of the asylum. Thanks to his hard work, the structure now responds to Alice's will, becoming a place from which it is impossible to escape without her consent. However, Alice has imprisoned the mad inventor in the Basement, keeping him alive for future bedlam expansion projects. Driven to madness by loneliness, Hatta has built two Automata (a Rabbit and a Lizard) as pretend tea companions."},"flags":{"scenarioId":"wonderbedlam","role":"imprisoned-inventor","location":"basement","companions":["rabbit-automaton","lizard-automaton"]}}
{"_id":"LizardAutomaton","name":"Lizard Automaton","type":"npc","img":"icons/creatures/magical/construct-iron-stomping-green.webp","system":{"npcType":"adversary","oppositionLevel":5,"isMainNPC":true,"attributes":{"soma":{"current":0,"max":0},"wounds":{"current":0,"max":3,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}}},"descriptors":["I am an automaton in the service of Hatta Carter","Thanks to my large tail I can perform several actions at the same time"],"gifts":[{"name":"Tail","description":"The Automaton always acts twice, once with its front legs and once with its long tail, but cannot focus both its actions on the same target."}],"background":"The second automaton built by Hatta Carter during his imprisonment in the Basement of Wonder. Created as a companion for lonely tea parties, this mechanical lizard is equipped with a powerful tail that allows it to perform multiple actions simultaneously. More robust than its Rabbit counterpart, it serves as both companion and guardian to the mad inventor."},"flags":{"scenarioId":"wonderbedlam","role":"automaton-guardian","creator":"hatta-carter","location":"basement"}}
{"_id":"RabbitAutomaton","name":"Rabbit Automaton","type":"npc","img":"icons/creatures/magical/construct-iron-stomping-yellow.webp","system":{"npcType":"adversary","oppositionLevel":5,"isMainNPC":false,"attributes":{"soma":{"current":0,"max":0},"wounds":{"current":0,"max":2,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}}},"descriptors":["I am an automaton in the service of Hatta Carter","Thanks to my strong legs I can make incredible jumps and crush everything when landing"],"gifts":[{"name":"Leap","description":"When it acts, the Automaton can free itself from any engagement with ease by jumping away. If it lands on a victim, it increases its OL by 1 for the attack and if it inflicts 1 Wound, the target will also be knocked to the ground."}],"background":"One of two automatons built by Hatta Carter during his imprisonment in the Basement of Wonder. Created out of loneliness to serve as a pretend tea companion, this mechanical rabbit is equipped with powerful legs that allow it to make devastating leaps. It serves its creator faithfully, defending him from any who would disturb his solitude."},"flags":{"scenarioId":"wonderbedlam","role":"automaton-guardian","creator":"hatta-carter","location":"basement"}}
